# turn column names to lowercase
df = df.rename(columns={i: i.lower() for i in df})

Как мы можем видеть, поле claim_speciality может содержать одинаковые значения в разном регистре, поэтому приведем значения этого поля к одному регистру

In [9]:
df['claim_specialty'] = df['claim_specialty'].apply(lambda x: x.strip().lower() if not pd.isna(x) else x)

In [14]:
def month_year_string_repr(row: pd.Series) -> str:
    month = row.month
    year = row.year
    return f"{year} - {'0' if month < 10 else ''}{month}"


df['year_month'] = df[['month', 'year']].apply(month_year_string_repr, axis=1)

In [20]:
# total_paid_amout of each payer per month
payer_x_date_sum = pd.pivot_table(data=df, columns='payer', index='year_month', values='paid_amount', aggfunc=np.sum).fillna(0)
payer_x_date_total = pd.pivot_table(data=df, columns='payer', index='year_month', values='paid_amount', aggfunc=np.size).fillna(0)

In [23]:
payers = df['payer'].unique()
In [24]:
fig, axs = plt.subplots(5, 2, figsize=(15, 25))
# get subplots objects to flat list

axs = iter(ax for row in axs for ax in row)
for payer in payers:
    ax = next(axs)
    ax2 = ax.twinx()
    ax.plot(payer_x_date_sum[payer])
    ax.set_ylabel('sum')
    ax2.set_ylabel('count')
    ax2.plot(payer_x_date_total[payer], color='red')
    ax.set_title(payer)
    ax.grid()
    plt.setp(ax.xaxis.get_majorticklabels(), rotation=75)


plt.subplots_adjust(
    wspace=0.3, 
    hspace=0.4
)

# Top 10 claim specialty per each payer
In [28]:
fig, axs = plt.subplots(5, 2, figsize=(15, 25))

# get subplots objects to flat list
axs = iter(ax for row in axs for ax in row)

for payer in payers:
    data = df[df['payer'] == payer].groupby(['claim_specialty']).size()
    data = data.sort_values(ascending=False).head(10)
    # display(data.head())
    ax = next(axs)
    ax.bar(height=data, x=data.index)
    ax.set_title(payer)

    plt.setp(ax.xaxis.get_majorticklabels(), rotation=70)
plt.subplots_adjust(
    wspace=0.15, 
    hspace=0.9
)
In [29]:
from collections import Counter
In [30]:
def most_common_value(x: pd.Series):
    return Counter(x).most_common(1)[0][0]
    

payer_x_claim = pd.pivot_table(data=df, columns='payer', index='year_month', values='claim_specialty', aggfunc=most_common_value)
